<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3147683" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="40"><variable id="footnote_with_line"><link href="text/swriter/guide/footnote_with_line.xhp" name="Spacing Between Footnotes">Spacing Between Footnotes</link>
</variable></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3145808" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="39">If you want to increase the spacing between footnote or endnote texts, you can add a top and bottom border to the corresponding paragraph style.</paragraph>
<list type="ordered">
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3155603" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="41">Click in a footnote or endnote.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3155620" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="42">Choose <emph>Format - Styles and Formatting</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3154251" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="43">Right-click the Paragraph Style that you want to modify, for example, "Footnote", and choose <emph>Modify</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3155884" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="45">Click the <link href="text/shared/01/05030500.xhp" name="Borders"><emph>Borders</emph></link> tab.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3147110" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="51">In the <emph>Default </emph>area, click the <emph>Set Top and Bottom Borders Only</emph> icon.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3150931" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="52">In the <emph>Line</emph> area, click a line in the <emph>Style </emph>list.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3150961" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="53">Select "White" in the <emph>Color </emph>box. If the background of the page is not white, select the color that best matches the background color.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3150519" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="50">In the <emph>Spacing to contents</emph> area, clear the <emph>Synchronize</emph> check box.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3150709" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="47">Enter a value in the <emph>Top </emph>and <emph>Bottom </emph>boxes.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3150740" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="48">Click <emph>OK</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
</list>
